-----------
TUTORIAL 04
-----------

This is a program that counts 0-9 on a 7-segment when the input logic is low.

Note:

- 7-segment pins

     g f x a b
     | | | | |
    -----------        a
    |         |       ----
    |         |    f | g  | b
    |         |       ----
    |         |    e | d  | c
    |         |       ---- *
    -----------            dp
     | | | | |
     e d x c dp

    x = common

*Task* Responsive Button
- Modify the given code so that counting can stop at any number
*Task* Up/down Counter
- Modify the given code so that the counting can be up OR down
- hint: need a switch for select
